title: So Cal Prep Legends Girls Athlete of the Week: Sydney Suarez, Saugus
text:
SO CAL PREP LEGENDS GIRLS ATHLETE OF THE WEEK
Name: Sydney Suarez
School: Saugus
Sport: Cross country
Year: Senior
Noteworthy: Suarez led a strong Saugus showing at the Santa Clarita Valley Invitational on Saturday at Lake Castaic Park, covering the three-mile course in 18 minutes, 11 seconds for a third-place finish and the top California mark. Her performance helped Saugus nail down the team title despite missing two regular runners.
What is So Cal Prep Legends? The best athletes in Southern California will be honored at an end-of-the-school-year awards show. For more details visit socalpreplegends.com, where you can also vote for the SoCal Athletes of the Week, as well as Play of the Week.
